Netflix: Hopper is alive


Everyone/Fans: we know already


Me: How is he gonna escape and find El, Dustin, Will, Max, Mike, Steve, Nancy, Joyce, Jonothan, Murray, and Lucas


My guess on the plot of the first episode(s): Murray will still have some hope and try to find hopper. He ends up finding the secret Russian thingy and talks in Russian to get passed the guards, ends up sneaking out Hopper and almost gets caught. They get back to Hawkins and do some big boy brain thinking just to find out that the train track Hopper was helping to build is the track that will be how they ship the stuff to get the portal to open in the new area.




@Stranger Things beat that
